{"tid":2299091,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以講好啲啲英文","createTime":"2020-11-24T13:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T08:09:26.000Z","uid":231125,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8f807a6105400a04051c458100b958e28f9739","tid":2299091,"uid":231125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"睇Netflix對白或者同外國人講嘢聽得明九成<br />\n但係到自己講嘅時候永遠都係講得唔好<br />\n永遠都仲係淨係可以用啲好簡單嘅詞彙來表達自己意思<br />\n究竟有咩方法可以講得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22232f794feeb70e5d40067a5c082fbdf6759cda","tid":2299091,"uid":364114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"講多啲英文咪好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f56d5d19dc72881ed0f96c5132c7d7d2fed122","tid":2299091,"uid":54721,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"去英國住"},{"pid":"3f381bdf97172d59b9e03d85e318956466ee8d97","tid":2299091,"uid":373689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"咁人哋聽唔聽得明你想表達啲咩？"},{"pid":"6552c834f221dc52356f4d3a6c7ad58025adb034","tid":2299091,"uid":231125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f381bdf97172d59b9e03d85e318956466ee8d97","tid":2299091,"uid":373689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"咁人哋聽唔聽得明你想表達啲咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"聽得明 <br />\n有用app 買package 同外國人上堂<br />\n但係覺得自己好似講左好多年都唔係好流利<br />\n無咩進步過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc63383217ad5a33bf8c3a69c06f989ea5b52845","tid":2299091,"uid":123765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"口語簡單詞彙就夠架啦 寫作就話姐"},{"pid":"30d066bbecb98fa4b445c02324aa926f117e5b2a","tid":2299091,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"去外國住2-3年"},{"pid":"da4758275f0bd8cb025109d409e439cfc667fdd7","tid":2299091,"uid":383621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"聽英文歌，睇多啲電影"},{"pid":"abcf90208deb111a012812762ff45b74489b23db","tid":2299091,"uid":101307,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"去外國住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係外國住左十零年(係學校冇讀過書 想屈我有學過grammar都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)講英文流利過香港大部分人 搵香港人教英文本身就戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你學法文會想跟法國肉腸學 學西文都想跟西人學原汁原味有口音嘅外語啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd9c80095270dfa3280ada21216d03680ee74c8","tid":2299091,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:55:38.000Z","msg":"又一個睇咗當學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1c56e50f1cf470c129e5cfe1f0b749f957fb3d","tid":2299091,"uid":329218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e8f807a6105400a04051c458100b958e28f9739","tid":2299091,"uid":231125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"睇Netflix對白或者同外國人講嘢聽得明九成<br />\n但係到自己講嘅時候永遠都係講得唔好<br />\n永遠都仲係淨係可以用啲好簡單嘅詞彙來表達自己意思<br />\n究竟有咩方法可以講得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T19:35:50.000Z","msg":"Pepe家族相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己語言能力算唔錯<br />\n雖然英文grammar唔算好好，vocabulary唔算多，但個人好夠膽講，而且識用simple english表達（簡單唔代表唔好，最緊要準確表達想講嘅野）。雖然有時會唸左中文先，但個腦都轉得幾快。<br />\n<br />\n宜家翻工有時要用英文又覺得自己有進步<br />\n<br />\n我覺得最緊要都係講得自然同埋咬字可以準確d,可能我以前有學古典聲樂，唱過英文，意大利文果d，所以咬字都幾標準。如果你中意唱歌可以試下練英文歌。"},{"pid":"4c978f612866634d61e6ce57cec4cf51076abb46","tid":2299091,"uid":79377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T23:55:07.000Z","msg":"我覺得就最好真係有朋友可以一齊陪講 但我都揾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5381825b98626bfcf545af782d19dec28957a2fc","tid":2299091,"uid":258097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T00:35:47.000Z","msg":"等報名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入面大把機會俾你日講夜講<br />\n<br />\n黃絲英文班，現正招生！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2e25cb93ed6282b11bb370697a842007a405be1","tid":2299091,"uid":73089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6552c834f221dc52356f4d3a6c7ad58025adb034","tid":2299091,"uid":231125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f381bdf97172d59b9e03d85e318956466ee8d97","tid":2299091,"uid":373689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"咁人哋聽唔聽得明你想表達啲咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"聽得明 <br />\n有用app 買package 同外國人上堂<br />\n但係覺得自己好似講左好多年都唔係好流利<br />\n無咩進步過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有直接同鬼佬傾 但好似無乜進步 <br />\n當然又唔係話好多堂 一星期一兩個鐘 但都半年<br />\n成日唔記得啲字 講又好急 會亂"},{"pid":"312b3c15fbf9a3cafd702b7e9dac1dfd311a0cfc","tid":2299091,"uid":79377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2e25cb93ed6282b11bb370697a842007a405be1","tid":2299091,"uid":73089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6552c834f221dc52356f4d3a6c7ad58025adb034","tid":2299091,"uid":231125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f381bdf97172d59b9e03d85e318956466ee8d97","tid":2299091,"uid":373689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"咁人哋聽唔聽得明你想表達啲咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"聽得明 <br />\n有用app 買package 同外國人上堂<br />\n但係覺得自己好似講左好